{"word":"παραθεωρέω","slug":"παραθεωρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παραθεωρέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to examine</i> a thing <i>beside</i> another, <i>compare</i>, <el>τινὰ πρός τινα</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to look slightly at, overlook, neglect</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}